  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500740/extras/6c273ef7455e9d49821866aad24b9e9f.avif?t=1773959619\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Now with hats!\"</i>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the world's greatest Snail MMO! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wanted to be a snail? Now you can be! Come along, bring a snail-y friend or two, and join us! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore </strong>the vast (low poly) Snearth with Snail Friends!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join</strong> monthly Snail Parties! 🐌🐌🐌🥳🥳🥳🐌🐌🐌 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MMOS</strong> (Massive Multiplayer Online Snails)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SaaS</strong> (Snails as a Service)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wear</strong> a hat (or not, this is <i>your simulation</i>)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>BECOME</strong></i> a snail (in a simulation)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Join</strong></i> a (sluggishly) growing community!  <br>Link to Discord is on the right-hand side!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will there be <strong><i>Slug DLC???</i></strong> (yes! it's available now!)!   </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thanks so much for the feedback from our feedback forms!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I am surprised at how fun that game is for how slow paced it is!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I have almost 60 hours and am still enjoying all the fun stuff the dev does. He is so active in his own community and is an absolute joy to talk too!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I think it's fostered such a great and inclusive community!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Epic game, 10/10, great job\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Perfection in snail form\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Its a really fun game and im glad i stumbled upon it!\"</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1500740/extras/6c273ef7455e9d49821866aad24b9e9f.avif?t=1773959619\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>\"Now with hats!\"</i>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to the world's greatest Snail MMO! </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Have you ever wanted to be a snail? Now you can be! Come along, bring a snail-y friend or two, and join us! </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore </strong>the vast (low poly) Snearth with Snail Friends!  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Join</strong> monthly Snail Parties! 🐌🐌🐌🥳🥳🥳🐌🐌🐌 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MMOS</strong> (Massive Multiplayer Online Snails)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>SaaS</strong> (Snails as a Service)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Wear</strong> a hat (or not, this is <i>your simulation</i>)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>BECOME</strong></i> a snail (in a simulation)!  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>Join</strong></i> a (sluggishly) growing community!  <br>Link to Discord is on the right-hand side!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Will there be <strong><i>Slug DLC???</i></strong> (yes! it's available now!)!   </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thanks so much for the feedback from our feedback forms!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I am surprised at how fun that game is for how slow paced it is!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I have almost 60 hours and am still enjoying all the fun stuff the dev does. He is so active in his own community and is an absolute joy to talk too!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"I think it's fostered such a great and inclusive community!\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Epic game, 10/10, great job\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Perfection in snail form\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Its a really fun game and im glad i stumbled upon it!\"</p>",
